## Featured Projects

### Autonomous Mobile Robot Control System

Autonomous mobile robot capable of obstacle avoidance, line following and autonomous navigation using embedded control techniques.

### DC Motor Generator Monitoring System

Monitoring platform for coupled DC motors capable of measuring voltage, current, electrical power and operating efficiency in both motor and generator modes.

### RF Impedance Matching Systems

Laboratory projects involving impedance matching using Smith Charts, Quarter-Wave Transformers and Open-Circuit Stubs, supported by MATLAB and QUCS simulations.

